{"published time": "2024-03-22T12:00:00+08:00", "images": ["https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg?w=683", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png?w=768", "https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png?w=768"], "content": "<div class=\"entry-content\">\n <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">\n  <em>\n   Por meio deste, publicamos uma tradu\u00e7\u00e3o n\u00e3o oficial de\n   <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/tribunal-popular-junco-maranhao/\">\n    Um artigo publicado\n   </a>\n   Eu uma democracia da Nova (e).\n  </em>\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n  <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6809\" data-attachment-id=\"6809\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"billede-6\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png\" data-orig-size=\"768,510\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/billede-6-13/\" height=\"510\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png?w=768\" srcset=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-6.png?w=768\" width=\"768\"/>\n </figure>\n <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">\n  Nos dias 9 e 10 de mar\u00e7o, o Tribunal Popular vitorioso contra paisagens e crimes baseados em terras foram realizados na vila de Vilela em Junco do Maranh\u00e3o. Aqui, advogados populares, pesquisadores, sindicalistas e jornalistas estaduais de outras regi\u00f5es do pa\u00eds participaram do comit\u00ea de julgamento do tribunal.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">\n  O Tribunal tamb\u00e9m teve a participa\u00e7\u00e3o de v\u00e1rias organiza\u00e7\u00f5es, como o Un\u00e3o Das Comunidades Em Luta e o Coletivo Estudantil Fillos do POVO, que organizou os alunos para participar do evento. O l\u00edder campon\u00eas\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/ma-luiz-vila-nova-memorias-da-vida-e-da-luta-de-um-militante-foi-relancado-em-evento-na-ufma/\">\n   Luiz Vila Nova\n  </a>\n  Tamb\u00e9m participou do evento.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\" data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":159656698,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com\\/2024\\/03\\/22\\/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao\\/\"}'>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6812\" data-attachment-id=\"6812\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6812\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"3-768\u00d7510-1\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"768,510\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/3-768x510-1/\" height=\"510\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg?w=768\" srcset=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/3-768x510-1.jpg?w=768\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6811\" data-attachment-id=\"6811\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6811\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"2-768\u00d7512-1\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"768,512\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/2-768x512-1/\" height=\"512\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg?w=768\" srcset=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/2-768x512-1.jpg?w=768\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">\n  Em todo o audit\u00f3rio, as bandeiras da organiza\u00e7\u00e3o adornavam as bandeiras e banners com slogons sobre a luta pela redistribui\u00e7\u00e3o de terras. Bem na estrada de acesso pendurou um banner \u00bb\n  <strong>\n   Fora com o trabalho de terra! Para o t\u00edtulo de nossos pertences!\n  </strong>\n  \"O tom ocorreu no evento. Dentro do audit\u00f3rio, havia outros banners que condenaram as priva\u00e7\u00f5es do solo, minerando em larga escala e pediam a unidade camponesa. As assinaturas vieram de ocupantes de v\u00e1rias comunidades como Gleba Campina, Povoado Vilela, Caranandeua e Jaraquara Communities e a Associa\u00e7\u00e3o de Campon\u00eas Povoado de Maracacuera no munic\u00edpio de Carutapera.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\" data-carousel-extra='{\"blog_id\":159656698,\"permalink\":\"https:\\/\\/socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com\\/2024\\/03\\/22\\/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao\\/\"}'>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6815\" data-attachment-id=\"6815\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6815\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"4-2\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg?w=683\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg?w=200\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"683,1024\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/4-2-8/\" height=\"1024\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" src=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg?w=683\" srcset=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/4-2.jpg?w=683\" width=\"683\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6816\" data-attachment-id=\"6816\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6816\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"5-blur-768\u00d7527-1\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp\" data-orig-size=\"768,527\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/5-blur-768x527-1/\" height=\"527\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp?w=768\" srcset=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/5-blur-768x527-1.webp?w=768\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6814\" data-attachment-id=\"6814\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-id=\"6814\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"6-blur-768\u00d7510-1\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp\" data-orig-size=\"768,510\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/6-blur-768x510-1/\" height=\"510\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp?w=768\" srcset=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/6-blur-768x510-1.webp?w=768\" width=\"768\"/>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">\n  Em uma das atividades do evento, os camponeses organizaram uma caravana de motocicleta para visitar Gleba Campina e investigar os crimes que o trabalho de barro cometeu l\u00e1.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n  <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6818\" data-attachment-id=\"6818\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"billede-7\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png\" data-orig-size=\"768,510\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/billede-7-12/\" height=\"510\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png?w=768\" srcset=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-7.png?w=768\" width=\"768\"/>\n </figure>\n <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">\n  Conforme dirigido pelo Tribunal Popular, as organiza\u00e7\u00f5es presentes para um dia de mobiliza\u00e7\u00e3o e luta contra o Estado da Lei de Maranh\u00e3o na Terra -depreciando em 1\u00ba de maio. A nota pode ser lida\n  <a href=\"https://medium.com/@comsolute/nota-conjunta-abaixo-a-lei-da-grilagem-35783ca1efa7\">\n   Na \u00edntegra aqui\n  </a>\n  .\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">\n  I en f\u00e6lles note skriver Solidarity Comit\u00ea de Solidariedade \u00e0 Luta pela Terra (COMSOLUTE) og Uni\u00e3o das Comunidades em Luta (UCL):\n  <em>\n   \"Este \u00e9 um evento vitorioso em todos os sentidos: estabelecendo e unindo uma agenda pol\u00edtica para defender os direitos humanos do povo; produzindo material jur\u00eddico em apoio \u00e0 causa das comunidades locais; agitando os presentes em torno da solidariedade com a luta pela terra\".\n  </em>\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">\n  A nota tamb\u00e9m d\u00e1 uma sauda\u00e7\u00e3o calorosa ao Coletivo Estudantil File, do Povo, que havia preparado um \u00f4nibus cheio de estudantes. Segundo os presentes, o Tribunal do Povo foi um marco no desenvolvimento do novo movimento estudantil em Maranh\u00e3o.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n  <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6820\" data-attachment-id=\"6820\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"billede-8\" data-large-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png?w=768\" data-medium-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png?w=300\" data-orig-file=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png\" data-orig-size=\"768,512\" data-permalink=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/billede-8-12/\" height=\"512\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png?w=768\" srcset=\"https://socialistiskrevolution.files.wordpress.com/2024/03/billede-8.png?w=768\" width=\"768\"/>\n </figure>\n <span id=\"wordads-inline-marker\" style=\"display: none;\">\n </span>\n</div>\n", "source": "https://socialistiskrevolution.wordpress.com/2024/03/22/brasilien-folkedomstolen-mod-jordberovelser-og-landbaserede-forbrydelser-afholdt-i-junco-do-maranhao/", "type": "article", "title": "Brasil: o Tribunal Popular contra os termos da Terra e os crimes baseados na terra mantidos em Junco do Maranh\u00e3o", "description": "Por meio deste, publicamos uma tradu\u00e7\u00e3o n\u00e3o oficial de um artigo publicado em uma Nova Democracia (e). Nos dias 9 e 10 de mar\u00e7o, o Tribunal Popular vitorioso contra paisagens e crimes baseados em terra ... tornou -se", "modified time": "2024-03-19T21:27:37+00:00", "author": ["socialistiskrevolution"], "categories": ["Uncategorized"], "source_name": "Socialistisk Revolution"}